widgets_values:
You: As a prompt generator for AI paintings, you can help me to write prompts related to scene paintings.
For example, write a detailed description of a painting of a Christmas scene, making sure to account for the season, the time of day, and the light.
BOT: panoramic view, distant view, flat view perspective, Christmas night, winter, the streets of the town are brightly lit, there is a huge Christmas tree in the square signed by the church, the Christmas tree is full of all kinds of gifts, the children are running around the Christmas tree, the fuchsia sky, the roof has a lot of snow, the colours are brilliant, the dreamy atmosphere, the fairy tale atmosphere. The whole picture is full of life, overall warm colours, purple tones are dominant, the highest quality, rich details, the highest quality.
You: Please follow the example above and help me write a detailed description of the scene painting, Note that only parts of the scene can be depicted, no protagonists are allowed, and you have to try to avoid depictions of the characters,making sure to account for the season, time and light. No need "Assistant:", just start the description with the subject：

YOU：You will act as a cue word generator for AI character drawing, helping me to write styling cues for female characters with different themes.
Example: Describe what a young woman would wear during the Christmas season.
Bot: A lovely girl wearing a red Christmas hat with a white fluffy pom-pom on her head and a red Christmas shawl with white fluffy trim on her upper body, she is smiling happily, holding a Christmas bell in her right hand and shaking it in front of her, her glasses are looking at the viewer, Gorgeous Costumes, Exquisite Clothing, Drawing of the Highest Quality, Richly Detailed, and of the Highest Quality.
You：Please help me describe in detail the appropriate clothing for a girl and when to gesture expressions based on the theme I have given you, only one character on the screen, do not describe the background content,
there is no need for "Assistant:"， just start the description with the subject：

LLM1

负责根据主题编写背景相关提示词

LLM2
根据性别判定模块输出的提示词，
结合绘画主题，
完成角色相关的提示词编写。

LLM3
结合绘画主题，
完成副文案的编写。
负责绘制背景图片，由于后续有高清放大模块，所以这里绘制一幅小图即可，以便节省时间，

PulID相关资源加载，用于传递人物面部特征。
插件地址：
https://github.com/cubiq/PuLID_ComfyUI
使用Layerstyle的“获取色调”节点，获取背景图像的主色调，以便为后续的“外发光”和“文本”提供匹配的色彩。

拼合图层，
将角色图像的背景删除，然后贴到背景上，同时增加外发光（以便区分层次），
后续的高清放大会弱化外发光，所以这里可以给的强一些。
——————
此处预留了一个“图像翻转”节点，如果对人物的朝向不满意，可以将它开启来调整人物朝向。

左侧输入你的人物图片，
右侧显示并存储最终完成图。

将拼合后的图像使用潜空间放大两倍重绘，使用AnyTest-ControlNet模型充当Tile来固化特征。改模型为完成CN，无需预处理器。、

下载地址：https://huggingface.co/2vXpSwA7/iroiro-lora/blob/main/test_controlnet2/CN-anytest_v4-marged.safetensors
使用说明：https://note.com/kokekokkosann/n/n46b3967fe895

——————
重新拉了一个单独的PulID，以便单独控制角色特征的灌入强度，这里你可以根据自己的喜好调节权重和起始时间，从而决定人物和原图的相似度。
为了避免角色特征影响背景图上的面部，PuLID上面接入了Mask。

将logo贴到画面上，
同时增加外发光
给生成的Logo增加描边以防止跟背景图像名都过于融合，导致层次区分不开。

利用LLaMA模型生成随机的绘画主题。
需要安装ExLLaMA插件。
https://github.com/Zuellni/ComfyUI-ExLlama

之后需要下载模型放到指定目录。
详情查看插件页说明。

将种子设为随机，既可以自动挂机不断输出不同主题的海报。、

将种子设为固定，可用于单个模块的调试。
——————
输出的文本会被提取第一行的内容作为最终的主题。
Under the glow of the Wild Night Moon, a group of friends embarked on a thrilling adventure through the enchanted forest.

性别判定模块，
负责根据输入图片识别人物性别，
以便给下一个LLM模块发出不同的指令。


反推器用的Layerstyle插件的LayerUtility: QWenImage2Prompt，

插件地址：https://github.com/chflame163/ComfyUI_LayerStyle
初次使用会自动下载反推模型，需翻墙，可能耗时较久。

利用Crystools插件的“切换字符串”节点，在手动输入的提示词和LLaMA自动生成的提示词之间做选择。

Crystools插件能在右侧控制栏上显示GPU占用情况，推荐使用：
https://github.com/crystian/ComfyUI-Crystools

——————
下部的节点用于将主题名称转换成没有特殊字符的格式，作为最终存储的文件名使用，
我设置了名为“AutoPoster”的文件名前缀，最终的输出图你会在ComfyUI\output\AutoPoster里找到。

——————
最右侧是Rgthree插件组的“禁用组”节点，可以用来控制组的开启和跳过。
https://github.com/rgthree/rgthree-comfy

https://huggingface.co/TheBloke/MythoLogic-Mini-7B-GPTQ/tree/main
